Q2) B) Write a program to set up a dynamic routing protocol such as RIP, EIGRP or OSPF.

Answer (Example: RIP Configuration):

enable
configure terminal

router rip
version 2
network 192.168.1.0
network 10.0.0.0
no auto-summary

exit

OR (EIGRP):

router eigrp 100
network 192.168.1.0
no auto-summary

OR (OSPF):

router ospf 1
network 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 area 0


